    Note over Client,Decode: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC plaintext
    Note over EPP: PD Decider triggers disaggregation<br/>Select prefill + decode pods
    EPP-->>Gateway: ProcessingResponse<br/>x-prefiller-host-port header
    Gateway->>PDSidecar: Forward to decode worker<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    PDSidecar->>Prefill: Prefill request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+ (SSRF validated)
    Prefill-->>PDSidecar: Prefill response + KV params
    PDSidecar->>Decode: Decode request with KV params<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
